{"id":232839314,"title":"#請益 啞鈴推薦","content":"最近在思考要不要買一組啞鈴放家裡\n能做居家訓練\n在蝦皮看到未來實驗室這組 不知道大家推不推\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e889403-f1ab-495b-9c04-d42c89399862/1280.jpeg\n\n我看它有連結桿 感覺也能拿來做臀推之類的動作\n\n但重量最多就是36kg的樣子 \n拿來做臀推練臀部是夠的嗎？\n\n之前有報健身房 但我的體質真的很會流汗\n只要一運動汗都是爆炸多的\n所以在外面運動我覺得有點尷尬😖\n比較偏向想在家做\n\n請問健身新手買啞鈴是ok的嗎\n希望大家可以給我一些建議 先謝謝大家了😭🙏","excerpt":"最近在思考要不要買一組啞鈴放家裡，能做居家訓練，在蝦皮看到未來實驗室這組 不知道大家推不推，我看它有連結桿 感覺也能拿來做臀推之類的動作，但重量最多就是36kg的樣子，拿來做臀推練臀部是夠的嗎？之前有","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"9b5213d6-4427-4a3c-b788-efa19493631c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-06T16:26:53.300Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-06T16:26:53.300Z","commentCount":12,"likeCount":7,"tags":[],"topics":["啞鈴","重訓","健身"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"健身","forumAlias":"fitness","school":"實踐大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":7}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e889403-f1ab-495b-9c04-d42c89399862/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"573b73c7-42c8-4a57-8bef-3af67540e4d1","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e889403-f1ab-495b-9c04-d42c89399862/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e889403-f1ab-495b-9c04-d42c89399862/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e889403-f1ab-495b-9c04-d42c89399862/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-01-06T16:26:53.300Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-06T16:26:53.300Z","width":360,"height":640},{"id":"573b73c7-42c8-4a57-8bef-3af67540e4d1","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e889403-f1ab-495b-9c04-d42c89399862/1280.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/0e889403-f1ab-495b-9c04-d42c89399862","th